            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>連展投控(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3710:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3710\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3710-TW</a>)30日13:22上漲0.64元，股價漲停報7.09元，委買4,000張、委賣358,000張，成交2,773張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要業務為一般投資業。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>連展投控(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3710:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3710\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3710-TW</a>)近5日股價上漲5.22%，櫃買市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>下跌1.04%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-65 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-65 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：0 張</li> <li>融資增減：0 張</li> <li>融券增減：0 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
