            "title": "盤中速報 - 昶和(1468)急拉3.08%報11.7元，成交77張",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>昶和(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1468:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1468\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1468-TW</a>)近5分K漲速3.08%，30日13:23報11.7元，成交77張，今日跌幅為0.85％。（註：漲跌速為5分K的漲跌幅）</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>昶和(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1468:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1468\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1468-TW</a>)近5日股價下跌1.67%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-12 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-11 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：-1 張</li> <li>融資增減：0 張</li> <li>融券增減：0 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
